guard~
a New Singase Guard~
A New Singase Guard stands alert to defend the village against intruders.~
The first thing you notice when you see him is his numerous battle decorations.
Obviously, he acted with great honor and courage in a great multitude of
military skirmishes. As you get past his decorations and look at him, you see
him standing alert and studying you to determine whether you are friend or foe.
He is tall for a gnome and wise beyond his years. His armor is impressively made
using the mose expensive and beautiful metals available while still keeping the
strength of the armor. Attacking him would be quite foolish.
~
